How many friends do you have?🧐
Zero? Humara bhi aisa hi tha! 
But then we found this crazy app called Misfits ( @_misfits_official ) 👀

When we shifted to Delhi NCR, our weekends = movie nights or TV. KAAFI BORING.
Cut to: weekend trips to Rishikesh with people who were strangers 2 months ago 😭✨

We joined the social deduction club on the app… and life legit changed.
Highly recommend if you’re tired of saying:
“Mere koi dost hi nahi hai…”
